# Q4: raw API outputs are gitignored; only aggregated/ is committed.
#
# The runners write raw per-run outputs to raw/, arm-a/, arm-b/, dryrun/, smoke/
# (and may add future arms/modes). Ignore every per-run directory so eval runs
# never dirty the working tree; keep only the curated aggregated/ results + this file.
/*
!.gitignore
!aggregated/
